絵本のように美しいパズルゲーム
挑戰手繪謎題 揭開幻想故事

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: You might get stuck the first time you play Gorogoa. But once the gears of your brain settle into the right configurations, you’ll see how smart this mix of art and perspective really is. Layers pile upon layers, doors transport you between realities, strange creatures and wild environments blend together into a fascinating interactive collage you’ll want to peel apart to discover what lies underneath.
